doomretro (a classic, refined DOOM source port)

DOOM Retro is the classic, refined DOOM source port for any PC. It
represents how I like my DOOM to be today, in all its dark and
gritty, unapologetically pixelated glory. I have strived to craft a
unique and cohesive set of compelling features, while continuing to
uphold my respect for that classic, nostalgic DOOM experience many
of us, after all this time, still hold dear.
